         </extensionElements>
         <text>SAP S/4HANA</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-DC6FA89C-4F5A-4D88-BBD3-408B0BECD7EB" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>1. Sales Area (Sales organization, Distribution channel, Division) should be available during sales order creation
2. Customer Pricing Procedure will be derived from "Sold to Party" 
3. Pricing Procedure will be derived from Sales Order type</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-7397DDBB-A053-40DF-804D-DAEC69D5F890" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/87e190e5800648088193185674a9aceb</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel align="left" bottom="false" left="false" ref="text_name" right="true" top="false" valign="middle" x="68.0" y="29.0"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SAP S/4HANA</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-78DBAAF3-D210-4C79-AE5E-D010FA3BA4D3" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/87e190e5800648088193185674a9aceb</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SAP S/4HANA</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-3EAED0DC-244F-4A15-8D31-F22F2DB9434C" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SO2: Resale Price is Copied from ZMPR -The material price. SO2 Will have a transfer price -A percentage on Resale price(Selling minus)</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-071FF6B0-EF50-4AAD-99CF-03B9C7647CAC" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Price Swamp will be executed as a Batch Run or executed by IT based on request</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-B6B7FCD6-2A2E-413F-83DB-E1F031F6E287" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Process Tower : OTC  Order to Cash
Process Group: O Order Management
Process: O-040-060D Determine Order Price and Conditions (LAFI)

</text>
      </textAnnotation>
   </process>
